\f0\b\fs48 Assignment:
\f2\b0\fs32 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\qc

\fs48 \cf0 Adapt any of the instruments provided in the code examples to produce single "cloud" of granular events when triggered by a GUI button, or by a keyboard event. The trigger will start a Routine that changes arguments in the instrument over time. It should have a discrete start and end, and be retriggerable, so that multiple starts produce new clouds that overlap. Play your instrument using your own samples and record a performance.
\fs32 \
